					<description><![CDATA[I just wanted everyone to know that I’ve had to pull the Clockwork Twist series from Smashwords, temporarily.  I’m having some technical issues with it.  The Kindle version and Paperbacks, however, aren’t going anywhere.  If the sudden lack of a Smashwords version causes any trouble for you at all, please let me know personally though [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I just wanted everyone to know that I’ve had to pull the Clockwork Twist series from Smashwords, temporarily.  I’m having some technical issues with it.  The Kindle version and Paperbacks, however, aren’t going anywhere.  If the sudden lack of a Smashwords version causes any trouble for you at all, please let me know personally though any social media avenue, and I’ll happily sort out the issue on a person-by-person bases.  Thanks!</p>
